SUMMARY:Shabbat Dinner
DESCRIPTION:Bay Area Jewish Singles Havurah\nPlease join us for our Shabbat dinner- Passover themed on April 3\, 2026. This will be held in San Jose\, at the home of one of our group members. The address will be shared closer to the date of the event.\n\nAttendance is limited to 20 individuals.\n\nYou're welcome to invite your single Jewish friends. Nevertheless\, we request that your guests register for the event on the meetup site directly. Thus\, the guest feature is disabled for this event.\n\nWe are asking for a donation of $3 per person to offset the cost of the MeetUp fees ( to be paid every 6 months).\n\nThis will be a potluck dinner- Passover themed as it will be the third night of Passover. We will NOT be having the formal Passover dinner nor reading the Haggadah\, just getting together to socialize.\n\nFood: If possible\, please bring foods that are typically served on Passover\, and please bring a dish large enough to serve 5-7 people. You are welcome to bring a bottle of wine as well\, if you would like. Please no pork\, bacon\, shellfish (shrimp\, clams etc.) nor bread products.\n\nWe will provide plates\, cups\, cutlery and non-alcoholic drinks. The stove\, microwave and oven will be available for you to reheat your dish. Nevertheless\, due to time constraints\, please bring the dish already prepared. Please write what you will bring in the comments section so that others can see.
